name: Rabbit Catcher
description:
My entry for AI and Games jam 2021

There is no sound.

Comes with a level editor, make your own levels! Edit mine! Make unwinnable levels! Go wild, there are no rules :p

Known issues:
The rabbits sometimes get stuck.
The rabbits move slower than you, but it doesnt always feel like that.
There is code to center the mouse after loading a level but for whatever reason, it doesnt do it.
You can stick the camera through the walls.
